ZH: 骚乱导致许多商店被打砸了。
EN: The riot resulted in many shops being smashed.

ZH: 这次骚乱中，许多人受了伤。
EN: Many people were injured in this riot.

ZH: 骚乱发生后，政府加强了警力。
EN: The government bolstered police presence after the riot.

ZH: 不要以为破坏公共财产是一种表达意见的方式，骚乱只会带来更多混乱。
EN: Vandalizing public property is not a way to express opinions; riots only bring more chaos.

ZH: 骚乱威胁到当地居民的生命安全。
EN: The riots pose a threat to the safety of local residents.

ZH: 骚乱的原因是政府不作为。
EN: The cause of the riot is government inaction.

ZH: 这座城市已经遭受了数天的骚乱。
EN: The city has been plagued by riots for several days.

ZH: 骚乱导致道路封锁，交通瘫痪。
EN: The riots led to road closures, halting traffic.

ZH: 警方设法平息了骚乱。
EN: The police managed to quell the riot.

ZH: 我们不能让骚乱继续下去。
EN: We cannot let the riot continue.

ZH: 骚乱使整个城市陷入恐慌之中。
EN: The riot plunged the entire city into panic.

ZH: 政府宣布进入紧急状态以遏制骚乱。
EN: The government declared a state of emergency to control the riot.

ZH: 暴徒们利用骚乱掩护自己的犯罪行为。
EN: The rioters took advantage of the riot to cover up their criminal activities.

ZH: 骚乱带来的破坏将耗费数额可观的修复费用。
EN: The destruction caused by the riot will incur substantial repair costs.

ZH: 骚乱爆发后，社会秩序陷入混乱。
EN: After the riot broke out, social order descended into chaos.

ZH: 出动军队镇压骚乱是政府的唯一选择。
EN: Deploying the military to suppress the riot is the government's only choice.

ZH: 骚乱使得投资者失去了信心。
EN: The riot caused investors to lose confidence.

ZH: 骚乱引发了全国范围的关注。
EN: The riot sparked nationwide attention.

ZH: 骚乱的影响会长期持续下去。
EN: The impact of the riot will be long-lasting.

ZH: 骚乱抵制暴力，维护社会安宁。
EN: Riots resist violence and maintain social peace.
